# Implementation Plan - PCL-Inspired Features

## Goal
Implement personalization features and enhanced launch settings inspired by PCL (Plain Craft Launcher) to improve user experience and customization.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Data Model (`AppConfig.cs`)
Update [AppConfig](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/ConfigService.cs#8-19) to include new settings:
- `BackgroundImagePath`: Path to custom background image.
- `BackgroundOpacity`: Opacity of the background image/overlay.
- `BlurEffectRadius`: Blur intensity for the background.
- `LauncherVisibility`: Enum (KeepOpen, Hide, Close).
- `ProcessPriority`: Enum (Normal, High).

### 2. ViewModel ([MainViewModel.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/ViewModels/MainViewModel.cs))
- Add `ObservableProperty` for `BackgroundImageSource` (BitmapImage).
- Add `ObservableProperty` for `BackgroundOpacity` and `BlurEffectRadius`.
- Implement `LoadBackground()` method to load image from config or fallback to default.
- Add `PickBackgroundImageCommand`.
- Add `UpdatePersonalizationCommand` to refresh settings.

### 3. UI - Main Window ([MainWindow.xaml](file:///c:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/MainWindow.xaml))
- Bind `Image.Source` to `MainViewModel.BackgroundImageSource`.
- Bind `Image.Effect` (BlurEffect) to `MainViewModel.BlurEffectRadius`.
- Bind Overlay Opacity to `MainViewModel.BackgroundOpacity`.

### 4. UI - Settings Page ([SettingsPage.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/SettingsPage.xaml))
- **New Section: Personalization**
    - **Background Image**: File picker ("Open Folder", "Select Image").
    - **Blur Slider**: Adjust blur radius (0-50).
    - **Opacity Slider**: Adjust overlay opacity (0-1).
- **Update Launch Section**
    - **Launcher Visibility**: ComboBox (Keep Open, Hide, Close).
    - **Process Priority**: ComboBox.

### 5. Launch Logic ([LaunchService.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/LaunchService.cs))
- Implement `LauncherVisibility` logic:
    - If `Hide`: Hide window on launch, show on exit.
    - If [Close](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/VersionSelectorDialog.xaml.cs#357-362): Close application on launch.
- Implement `ProcessPriority` logic when starting the process.

## Verification Plan
### Manual Verification
- **Background**:
    - Select a custom image. Verify it updates immediately.
    - Adjust sliders. Verify real-time updates.
    - Restart app. Verify settings persist.
- **Launch**:
    - Set visibility to "Hide". Launch game. Verify window hides. Close game. Verify window reappears.
    - Set visibility to "Close". Launch game. Verify app closes.

### Automated Tests
- None (UI-heavy features).
